title: Hour 1 - Warriors Paying the Tax, Price Too High To Move Durant
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Warriors Paying the Tax, Price Too High To Move Durant
description:
Dan reminds everyone exactly how much the Warriors doled out in luxury tax after their latest championship season, and thinks Kevin Durant is too expensive for the Nets to move.
